Two States Most Impacted by Harvey

histogram(data.State)

ylabel('Number of Events')

Conclusions and Recommendations

The analysis above extracts out some of the places, which are most affected by Harvey. They were the following:
  • Collin
  • Harris
  • Tarrant
  • Greene
  • Jackson
  • Barry
  • Galvestom
  • Fort Bend
  • Henderson
  • Howell
  • Carter
  • Barton
They all belong to Texas and Missouri, the most affected states.
